      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i feel like u don't get it. it's not just about being \"busy\". it's like... i'm a ghost. i go through the motions and the world just keeps turning without a glitch. if i just vanished tomorrow, the silence would probably be the same as it is now. it's almost like it would be easier to just... stop. just let the silence take over completely. it feels more honest than trying to pretend i matter.",
